data.description: Step into your dream home! Nestled on a charming 3/4 acre lot, this exquisite property boasts a delightful four-bedroom, two-bathroom sanctuary with a spacious one-car garage and a breezeway that beckons you to unwind and savor the tranquility of the outdoors. As you approach the front door, you are greeted by the allure of a meticulously maintained exterior that exudes charm and curb appeal. The allure of the property is further enhanced by the semi-finished basement, offering ample space for relaxation, entertainment, or any other activities you desire. Upon entering, you are welcomed by the warmth of the updated HVAC system installed in 2022, ensuring your comfort throughout the seasons. The heart of the home, the kitchen, has been tastefully updated to reflect modern aesthetics while maintaining a timeless charm that is sure to inspire your culinary adventures. The four bedrooms provide ample space for your family and guests, each offering a cozy retreat for rest and rejuvenation. The two bathrooms are designed with both functionality and style in mind, offering convenience and comfort for your daily routines. Outside, the expansive 3/4 acre lot beckons you to explore and indulge in the beauty of nature, whether you choose to relax on the breezeway or enjoy outdoor activities in the spacious yard. This property is not just a house; it is a home where cherished memories are waiting to be made. Don't miss the opportunity to make this adorable abode your own and experience the joy of living in a space that seamlessly blends comfort, style, and functionality. Your dream home awaits!
